column2: Good clear day a little wind. not much
Lake was clear except for small pin head size green alge.. flooting around...     Cows on south end are at the

column1: lake daily doing their thing... Lots of smell their.
Cows were at the lake again as usual doing their duty.

column2: Cow in lake doing the business....
Cows still at edge of south west end of lake
Water is clear- to 15ft.  nice.   Their was a lot of Bullhead and Frogs dead along shore line suspect do to lots of snow on lake.

column1: Also- found two crayfish in lake...

column2: spotted two very large snapping turtles in lake.

column1: Spotted two black bear on shoreline.

column2: Lake is clear to 14 feet. Sunny day. Nice....Always have one Loon on lake. This year we have two. Babies...?????
lake about a 12-14 inchs higher then normal

column1: Lots of baby bullheads in lake.  Many schools swimming around.. have not noticed before- but- did not try to find either. Spring lake was very clear. about 14-15 feet now about 5 feet..(Cloudy)

column2: Lots of BULLHEAD schools number in the thousands...several schools..Is this good or bad....???
lots of bullhead.  fishing has been poor. The past 4 weeks. not sure how the Trout did over last winter.

column1: Lake water is high Water seems clear with some alge in the water...

column2: been fishing a lot on Crescent but- have not be getting any Trout Seems like a lot might have died over last winter.???. Their are a lot of Bullhead in the lake many schools of small bullhead.
nice sunny day. lake water is not clear like drinking water. but- it appear green when looking at the whole lake.

column1: if you take a bucket of water out it will look clear.  John Dow.

column2: Lake is very clear. Not sure what to call lake color as it is clear but- from a distance looks green.
lots of pollen dusting on the lake.

This year 2016  lake is very clear. With some alge  present. And clarity is at 9 to 10 feet.  Water clarity slowly goes down as you move disk..     ... Is there a reason for the clearer lake water on Crescent.     The bottom is very grassy....   With a lot more lily pads. in the lake....
notice over by boat landing a lot of green slimy moss. very stringy like thread.. its below and above the water...
water looks good secchi is at 7.5 feet.. two weeks age it was at 9 feet..
water is clear to 3.6 feet. water does not look green but- dirty.???
1. Lake is clean to 12 to 13 ft. Small amount of green dots in water but- very clear looking.

column1: 2. Very few lilly pads for this time of year. Bass lake about the same.
3. Big black BEAR come to our house last night. Could not scare HIM AWAY. HE EAT ALL BIRD FEEDERS AND
COULD CARE LESS THAT WE WERE MAKING NOISE TRYING TO SCARE HIM AWAY. Held his ground.
4.  Two loons on lake one large and one small. both came at the same time this year. One has a hard time getting

column2: We live on this lake and we had a bear in our bird feeders. We could not chase him away. He was not scared at all of us.
